During the military presence of the Esmers on [[Twinsun]] Esmer troops and robots were guarding the streets, many public places, like [[Chez Luc]] and [[Miss Bloop's Private Museum]] were closed, along with the ferry service.

Mine fields were seen on [[Desert Island]] making it hard not to use the guarded streets.

With the prepared destruction of Twinsun with the [[Emerald Moon base|lunar reactors]], however, more and more Esmers left the planet, bringing themselves out of danger.

